      "text": {
        "zh": "尿痛/尿频通常会先做尿常规来判断是否有感染或血尿；如果伴发热或腰痛，医生也可能考虑进一步验血或影像来排除肾盂肾炎或结石等。",
        "en": "Dysuria/frequency is often evaluated with urinalysis. With fever or flank pain, blood tests or imaging may be considered for pyelonephritis or stones."
